Subject: SOP Attention Memory Codec

Description: Contract for storing and recalling thinking nodes as visual/color-routed optical instruction streams with explicit reconstruction boundaries.

@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_sop_attention_memory_codec\Dictated_SOP_Attention_Memory_Codec_Source.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPProgramBookends.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPPhotonicFrameStream.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPColorChannelVocabulary.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPOpticalTransformAlgebra.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPSemanticVideoDigest.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPMultitrackChannelCompression.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPFiberFPGABridge.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SecurityHonestyGovernance.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\BoundaryFacultyInspection.sop
